proposal: Diving into the world of decentralized AI on Web3 sounds like a journey to the future, and with only 20 holders in the ETH network, it feels like an exclusive club! 🚀 Why not expand this vision with tools that not only share revenue but empower your community? Imagine deploying your own DEX or engaging in a blockchain lottery, all while staying true to your decentralized roots. Let's make the future accessible to everyone, one tool at a time.
